OL,3,CBereaved mother vows to keep fighting
OL,4,Cfor maternity safety
OL,6,FThe parents of a baby girl who should
OL,7,Fhave celebrated her sixteenth birthday
OL,8,Fthis weekend say they won't stop
OL,9,Fcampaigning for maternity safety.
OL,11,FRichard Stanton and Rhiannon Davies
OL,12,Flost their daughter, Kate, just six
OL,13,Fhours after she was born due to
OL,14,Ffailings in maternity care at
OL,15,FShrewsbury and Telford NHS Trust in
OL,16,F2009.
OL,18,FIt took over three and a half years
OL,19,Ffor the couple to get an inquest and,
OL,20,Fwhen they did, it revealed a catalogue
OL,21,Fof failings in their baby's care.
