OL,6,FSaturday 1 March would have been the
OL,7,F16th birthday of Kate Stanton-Davies.
OL,9,FIn April 2016, the Trust apologised
OL,10,Fand said lessons would be learnt. But
OL,11,Fsoon after, another family reached out
OL,12,Fto Richard and Rhiannon to tell them
OL,13,Fthey found themselves in a similar
OL,14,Fsituation.
