OL,4,Cfor maternity safety
OL,6,FThe senior midwife had examined just
OL,7,Fover a thousand maternity cases and in
OL,8,Fher 2022 report, she said baby Kate's
OL,9,Fdeath was preventable and urgent
OL,10,Faction was needed to improve care both
OL,11,Fat the hospital and across the country.
OL,13,FIt's one of four major maternity
OL,14,Freviews to take place in England and
OL,15,Fthree years on, 65% of maternity units
OL,16,Fhave been found to be not safe by the
OL,17,Fmaternity watchdog.
