OL,11,FInspectors have warned that poor
OL,12,Fhealthcare is becoming normalised and
OL,13,FMPs called a meeting last week to
OL,14,Fdiscuss the maternity care crisis.
OL,16,FHelen Morgan, MP for North Shropshire
OL,17,F(Liberal Democrats) said: "They've
OL,18,Fconsistently highlighted safe
OL,19,Fstaffing, they've consistently
OL,20,Fhighlighted poor management culture
OL,21,Fand poor working environments.
