OL,6,F"They've highlighted a fixation with
OL,7,Fnot performing caesarean sections and
OL,8,Fproviding women with the medical help
OL,9,Fthey need when things are going wrong.
OL,11,F"There are a number of actions that
OL,12,Fneed to be sorted out, the government
OL,13,Fknow what they are, they need to
OL,14,Fimplement them."
